Duong’ ma Jerusalem biro yudo


1  In dala Jerusalem, a malo!

Rieny nikech lerni osechopo

kendo duong’ maler mar Ruoth Nyasaye oselor kuomi.


2  Kata obedo ni mudho biro umo piny,

mi ogendini bed e mudho mandiwa,

to Ruoth Nyasaye norieny kuomi,

mi duong’ne maler nonenre kuomi.


3  Ogendini gi ruodhigi nobi e lerni mathinyore.


4  Ting’ wang’i mondo irang koni gi koni.

Nyithindi duto chokore ka biro iri.

Adier, yawuoti biro koa kuma bor,

kaachiel gi nyigi, koik e bathe.


5  Kineno kamano to inibed mamor, mi chunyi pong’ gi ilo. Mwandu mogundho mag ogendini mopogore opogore nokelni gi yiedhi. 
6  Ngamia mang’eny moa Midian gi Efa nopong’ pinyi. Giduto ginia Sheba ka gikelo dhahabu kod ubani, kendo ka gipako Ruoth Nyasaye gi wer. 
7  Jamni duto mag Kedar nochokni. Rombe mag Nebayoth bende nobed jamni mitimogo misengni ma ayiego e kendona mar misango, mi duong’ maler mar Hekalu mara nomedre. 
8  Mago gin ang’o ma kwang’ ka boche polo, kata mahuyo ka akuche maduogo e odgigo? 
9  Gin yiedhi moa e pinje manie dhonembe kod chulni, ma biro ka yiedhi madongo mag Tarshish otelonigi. Gikelo yawuoti moa kuma bor, ka nigi dhahabu kod fedha, ma gibiro miyogo nying Ruoth Nyasaye, ma Ng’ama Ler mar Israel duong’, nimar osemiyi duong’.


10  A Jerusalem, jopinje mamoko ok nochak oger ohinga mari,

kendo ruodhigi nobed jotichni.

Kata obedo ni ne asandi malit ka an gi mirima kamano,

to koro asekechi, kendo ang’wononi.


11  

Dhorangeyeni biro siko koyaw,

kendo ok nochieggi godiechieng’ kata gotieno,

mondo ji okelni mwandu mag ogendini,

ka ruodhigi otelonigi.


12  Ogendini gi pinje motamore tiyoni biro lal nono,

mi kethre chuth.


13  Yien mabeyo mag Lebanon bende nokelni,

mondo omedgo duong’ maler mar Hekalu mara,

ma en raten tienda.


14  

Yawuot joma ne sandi biro miyi duong’.

Adier, joma ne chari biro kulore e tiendi.

Giniluongi ni ‘Dala Ruoth Nyasaye’,

kendo ni ‘Sayun Dala mar Ng’ama Ler mar Israel’.


15  Isebedo dala mojwang’ kendo ma ji ochayo, maonge ng’ama lim,

to koro abiro miyo ibedo dala man gi duong’ mosiko,

ma kelo ni ji mor ma ok rum.


16  Iniyud mwandu mag ogendini koda ka mago mag ruodhi.

Kamano ining’e ni an, Ruoth Nyasaye e jaresni.

Adier, jawarni en Ng’ama Nyalo Gik Moko Duto,

ma Nyasach Jakobo.


17  Kar mula anakelni dhahabu,

to kar nyinyo anakel fedha.

Kar yien anakel mula,

kendo kar kite anakel nyinyo,

bende anami jotendi tiyo gi kue kod tim makare.


18  Timbe mahundu ok nochak owinji kendo e pinyi,

kata mana tulo moro marach ok nochak omuoch machiegni kodi.

To iniluong ohinga mari ni, ‘Resruok.’

Dhorangeyeni to iniluong ni, ‘Pak.’


19  

Wang’ chieng’ ok nochak obedni ler mar odiechieng’,

kata due ok nochak orienyni gotieno,

to Ruoth Nyasaye ema nobedni ler mosiko.

Nyasachi nobedni duong’ maler


20  Wang’chieng’ ok nochak opodhi,

kendo dueyi bende ok notho,

nikech Ruoth Nyasaye ema nobedni ler mosiko,

mi ndaloni mar ywak norum.


21  Jogi duto nobed joma kare,

kendo piny nobed margi nyaka chieng’.

Ginichal gi bad yath ma an ema apidho gi lweta awuon,

mondo okelna duong’.


22  Ji manok nolokre gana apar,

kendo oganda matin nolokre oganda maduong’.

An Ruoth Nyasaye anami gino timre piyopiyo nono,

ka kindene ochopo.

